{"tid":1473853,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"公開撐警香港青年會成員資料","createTime":"2019-08-15T03:26:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T03:46:31.000Z","uid":189629,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9d0935619cf1e65b28e6057d0e3ed82b8ff988ce","tid":1473853,"uid":189629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:26:20.000Z","msg":"小女幾年前喺朋友介紹下同<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港新星青年會港島分會</span></span></strong>嘅成員食左餐飯，當時只為識朋友，並唔知道原來佢地絕大部份都係紅底親中人士，加入Wts個群組後一直無參加過佢地其他活動。<br />\n<br />\n老實講，本來小女我政治冷感，多一事不如小一事，但經過犬隻將女示威者底褲扯甩、地鐵開槍8.11事件之後，我真係好嬲！！！同大學同學出席機場「和你飛」嘅時候禁手機比我見到Le個會嘅人竟然Po出以下相片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nfyGfNR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnfyGfNR.jpg&h=27d484e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jo8bC1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjo8bC1b.jpg&h=e6434ef6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G8QUANS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG8QUANS.jpg&h=3e06f080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KGuRC1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKGuRC1e.jpg&h=d336bbdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w0W8FeA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw0W8FeA.png&h=1ad520c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rJiu87W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrJiu87W.png&h=f0e90183&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8z8nKGi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8z8nKGi.png&h=338d282b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7p27VNZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7p27VNZ.png&h=c33319a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0J4upGk.png\" 