x%2Fi%2F3z6P9ec.png&h=20e3438a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上有紅筆刪去電話同名嘅人同小女一樣，加入群組之後並無發聲支持同埋參與活動，但其牠已公開電話號碼嘅人皆已證實有出席過撐落活動。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家於凌晨/深夜時熱烈地致電以上電話，提佢地起身柯夜尿，並代表黨多謝佢地嘅付出及貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n以上只係新星<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">港島區分會</span></span></strong>嘅會員，喺其它分會嘅義士若果同我一樣睇唔過眼，歡迎公開埋佢地嘅資料。"},{"pid":"3726afc22a38a42799fd667b2cd18155161f4a47","tid":1473853,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:42:42.000Z","msg":"我地應該每星期搵一日，同一個時間一齊搭車入機場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468945</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a5d9bdaa10da24a2378a3a907fe214520f4f93d3","tid":1473853,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d70fd85a1ed1ad17d5b89a2e6f70547b3d5dda","tid":1473853,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:43:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihk